subject: Basketball
College Athletics
organizations: Virginia Polytechnic Institute and State University
lead_paragraph: Tyler Hansbrough was the heart of a spirited effort by the Tar Heels in a victory over a Virginia Tech team that needed to win to land a spot in the N.C.A.A. tournament.
